name: Select From and Till Leave date from Calendar

testSteps.description: 1: Select From and Till Leave date from Calendar ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=Apply, tab=Out Duty/Tour, fromDate=4/10/2022, toDate=4/10/2022})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "Apply" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
When User clicks on "Out Duty/Tour" Tab
Then Select "4/10/2022" From date and "4/10/2022" till Leave dates for Out Duty Tour
